      "text": "おはようございます\n星見プロの{user}さん",
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あっおはようございます、天動さん\n今日はレッスンですか？　うちの子達もなんです",
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね\n私達もこれからスタジオに向かいます",
      "startTime": 23.544979887083173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、あの……\nもしかして何か困っていますか？",
      "startTime": 28.57627449184656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "先ほどから\nキョロキョロしているようですけど……？",
      "startTime": 32.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、実は財布を落としたみたいで……",
      "startTime": 34.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nでしたら私も探すので、来た道を戻りましょう",
      "startTime": 40.30356063842773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え、天動さんが？　そんな、悪いですよ\nそれに、天動さんはレッスンがあるでしょう",
      "startTime": 48.02079174108803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それぐらい構いませんよ。遅刻した理由を\n説明すれば、みんな分かってくれますから",
      "startTime": 55.180352225899696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、今ここで困っている\n{user}さんを見捨てたりしたら",
      "startTime": 59.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれに怒られちゃいます",
      "startTime": 62.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "あの子達がここにいたら\nきっと同じようにお手伝いするはずですし",
      "startTime": 66.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、財布の中には免許証やクレジットカードなど\n大切なものが入っているんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 73.44160313531756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女は若手で一、二を争う人気グループのセンターだ）\n（俺の落とし物なんかで手を借りる訳にはいかない）",
      "startTime": 80.2333333350718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいって言ってるのに……",
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あっ、天動さん",
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、結構頑固なんですね",
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、気にしないで下さい\n私が勝手にやっていることですから",
      "startTime": 93.07258018478751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら君の方こそ頑固なんだけど……",
      "startTime": 95.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ私は{user}さんほどでは\nないですよ？",
      "startTime": 102.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、それじゃあ一緒にお財布を探しましょう",
      "startTime": 104.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（その前に、天動さんがレッスンに遅れる旨を）\n（スタジオに連絡しておいた方がいいだろう）",
      "startTime": 110.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（カバンの中に入っている携帯電話を漁り）\n（そこで、存在するはずのないものを発見してしまった）",
      "startTime": 116.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "どうかされましたか？",
      "startTime": 120.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、あの……財布ありました。カバンの中に……\nごめんなさい。普段ポケットに入れてるから、つい……",
      "startTime": 129.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　カバンの中にですか？",
      "startTime": 133.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "無事見つかったのなら、良かったですね？",
      "startTime": 136.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……いやあの、天動さん？\n怒らないんですか？",
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "ウッカリすることは、誰にでもありますよ\n私だってそうですし",
      "startTime": 148.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "ということなので、私が怒ることも\nあなたが謝る必要もありません",
      "startTime": 152.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
